    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-16">
      <h2 style="text-align:center">Background of the Environmental Risk Behavior</h2><br>
      <h4 style="text-align:center"> Plastic Pollution is the accumulation of plastic objects and particles like plastic bottles and much more in the Earth's environment that adversely affects Wildlife habitat, and Humans.Plastic pollution can effect Land, Waterways, and Oceans.</h4>
      <h4 style="text-align:center">Marine animals can become entangled in or ingest plastics causing suffocation, starvation and drowning.</h4><br>
     
      <h2 style="text-align:center">Possible Solutions</h2>
      <h4><li>Return single use bags to grocery stores for them to recycle</li></h4>
      <h4><li>Reduce use of plastic waste</li></h4>
      <h4><li>Conduct campaign /orientation in barangays on issues related to plastic pollution and help ake others aware of the problem</li></h4>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



